message.body: What time are you going to start the BBQ fire? If I come can I bring two of the untouched trays of food from yesterday's party?
Around 4 pm. And a big please, yes, and thank you for the wonderful food!!!!
I am so sorry i am terrible but I keep forgetting your street name !!!!
No I am leaving soon with Shenandoah. I kept googling cool lane. Forgot about the valley. We will need to heat up the chicken and the rice when we get there...
Thanks for the wonderful party. Sorry we came late and I wish I could have stayed a little longer. We both enjoyed it very much.
I am so very glad you came. Thank you!!!!!! Much love.
